@startuml
!include ../../styles/plantuml-theme.puml
title Online Store requirements analysis thread
skinparam nodesep 24
skinparam ranksep 35
skinparam defaultFontSize 13

rectangle "Stakeholder need\nNEED-25-01\nKnow promptly whether\nan order was accepted" as N #FFF2CC
rectangle "Functional requirement\nFR-25-01\nCreate one order and\nreturn its reference" as FR #DDEBF7
rectangle "Quality scenario\nQA-25-01\n95% within 2 seconds\nat forecast peak" as QA #DDEBF7
rectangle "Use case\nUC-25-01\nCheckout, decline\nand uncertain response" as UC #E2F0D9
rectangle "Conceptual model\nBasket, Order,\nPayment Attempt" as CM #E2F0D9
rectangle "Design response\nIdempotent order creation\nand status handling" as DR #E4DFEC
rectangle "Verification case\nVT-25-01\nPeak and retry tests" as VT #FCE4D6
rectangle "Evidence\nResults and stakeholder\nvalidation" as EV #FCE4D6

N -down-> FR : refined by
N -down-> QA : measured by
FR --> UC : clarified by
FR --> CM : uses concepts from
QA --> DR : drives
UC --> DR : informs
CM --> DR : constrains meaning of
DR --> VT : verified by
FR --> VT : assessed by
QA --> VT : measured by
VT --> EV : produces
EV ..> FR : feedback refines
EV ..> QA : feedback refines

legend bottom
Solid arrows show forward trace links.
Dotted arrows show iterative learning.
endlegend
@enduml

